node.text: This was the first Birthday Video we ever made for BUB, for her 2nd birthday in 2013. On that year I gifted BUB her very own talk show, Lil BUB’s Big SHOW. This year, we are giving her the promise that we will continue her good work in helping animals at risk by raising money for 5 amazing organizations. Today is our last chance to help make BUB’s intergalactic dreams come true by making a tax-deductible donation at the link in BUB's bio (https://giveli.st/lilbub/. You will also be entered to win her new commemorative book, and a trip for you and a friend to her hometown of Bloomington, IN! GOOD JOB BUB. #lilbub #bubsbig10th

node.text: It’s the second day of Lil BUB’s Big 10th Birthday Fundraiser! You can honor BUB’s memory with a single donation to be split between five AMAZING animal welfare organizations at the link in BUB's bio. Your donation will enter you to win BUB’s new Commemorative Book and a video chat with me and BUB’s siblings!  #missyoubub #goojobbbub #lilbub #bubsbig10th #bilbobubbins #scienceandmagic #thereisonlyoneBUB

node.text: Today is Lil BUB's Big 10th Birthday kickoff! She may now be in space, but we're still here on Earth continuing her good work by helping animals in need. As a gift to BUB and special needs pets nationwide, you can donate to Lil BUB's Big 10th Givelist Campaign at the link her bio. Your donation will be split equally between five of BUB's favorite animal welfare organizations (including ours), and every donation is entered to win one of four amazing prizes every day, for the next five days. Let’s make BUB proud! #bestjobbub #lilbub #BUBsBig10th
